{"tid":816846,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 泫雅俾cube炒咗！","createTime":"2018-09-13T04:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T17:00:48.000Z","uid":78983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e811d8339d363fcc0237b1a171e6539291434f20","tid":816846,"uid":78983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"泫雅、E'Dawn被CUBE娛樂辭退&hellip;「與藝人之間的信賴已經不可能恢復」<br />\n<br />\n今日（13日），CUBE娛樂發表官方聲明，由於和藝人的信任無法恢復，公司決定辭退泫雅和E'Dawn，並向一直陪伴兩位藝人的粉絲們致以真心感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於上月初（8月）傳出戀情的泫雅和E'Dawn，消息本經公司否認，隔天卻主動向大眾承認戀情，成為話題焦點。隨後，兩人所屬的特別企劃組合「Triple H」活動全面取消，E'Dawn也沒能從PENTAGON回歸歌壇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日（13日），CUBE娛樂發表官方聲明，公司決定辭退旗下藝人泫雅和E'Dawn。一直以來，公司在管理藝人方面把互相信賴和信任放在第一順位，經過多次討論與苦惱後，覺得和兩位藝人之間的信任已經不可能恢復，所以做出辭退的決定，也感謝一直陪伴兩位藝人的粉絲們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/amp/109277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Famp%2F109277&d=uWKPkhDhjQm3ykyRRWunqE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=7e4117b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/amp/109277</a>"},{"pid":"0d969dc201e43088923e2769e2c077c17277ba9e","tid":816846,"uid":2832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛，cube傻撚左？？"},{"pid":"03db2b5c3eab6ed321d60d434c2e8769489e01ab","tid":816846,"uid":190258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:19:38.000Z","msg":"戀愛大過天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b981a50d3782f47d085423f1823407fba3e4f07b","tid":816846,"uid":149852,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:23:27.000Z","msg":"cube 正式收皮"},{"pid":"6666a9d9fab7aba44fa920d83d0cfe46b8383738","tid":816846,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"c2a057ef2d1c3d151c62b5a653e487f7168439cd","tid":816846,"uid":78983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl